39:34.660 --> 39:36.580
If you zoom into the model, if you lift it up,

39:36.580 --> 39:37.900
if you look around, if you pick it up,

39:37.900 --> 39:40.340
you say, hey, this thing is kind of small to be the Millennium

39:40.340 --> 39:42.300
Falcon.

