41:54.140 --> 41:55.460
through something called thermal freeze out,

41:55.460 --> 41:57.460
that was the calculation that we asked the grad student

41:57.460 --> 42:00.580
to do over and over and over again.

42:00.580 --> 42:01.500
Why is it still here?

42:01.500 --> 42:02.740
